To build an run the Clock sample program follow these steps.

1.	SBE Clock/W
2.	Select <N>ew <P>rogram and enter - Clock
3.	Select <N>ew menu, <E>xe def and enter - Clock
4.	Select the Clock program
5.	Press ALT/L to link the program.
6.	You now must run the resource compiler
        Using the Microsoft Resource Compiler execute the following
	DOS commands.
	
	RC -r clock.rc
	RC clock.res
	
7.	Now you are ready to run the Clock demo program.
